\v 4 \x - \xo 5.4 \xt Tgt 66. 13,14.\x*\w Pathen|strong="H0430"\w* \w taengah|strong="H9997"\w* \w olcaeng|strong="H5088"\w* na \w caeng|strong="H5087"\w* \w vaengah|strong="H0834"\w* na \w thuung|strong="H7999"\w* \w ham|strong="H9997"\w* \w uelh|strong="H0309"\w* \w boeh|strong="H0408"\w*. Na \w caeng|strong="H5087"\w* \w bangla|strong="H0834"\w* a \w thuung|strong="H7999"\w* te aka \w ang|strong="H3684"\w* \w kah|strong="H9996"\w* \w kongaih|strong="H2656"\w* \w moenih|strong="H0369"\w*.  
